rows.label: tlk41300011_02_msg0001
rows.name:
There was a bidding war between an
Superbian and an Invidian just now.

rows.label: tlk41300011_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Even when it's the tiniest little thing,
they still find a way to be at each
other's throats.

rows.label: tlk41300011_02_msg0003
rows.name:
I just hope Superbia and Invidia's
stupid rivalry won't blow up into a
full-scale war.

rows.label: tlk41300011_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Only the smallest fraction of people
benefit when the world is at war,
after all...
